msgid "Activity Log"
msgstr "Aktivitätsprotokoll"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:165
msgid "General Settings"
msgstr "Allgemeine Einstellungen"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:172
msgid "Enable Contact Form 7 Protection"
msgstr "Contact Form 7-Schutz aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:178
msgid "Enable spam protection for Contact Form 7 submissions"
msgstr "Spam-Schutz für Contact Form 7-Übermittlungen aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:184
msgid "Enable Comments Protection"
msgstr "Kommentare schützen"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:190
msgid "Enable spam protection for comments"
msgstr "Spamschutz für Kommentare aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:196
msgid "Automatically Mark Pingbacks/Trackbacks as Spam"
msgstr "Pingback/Trackback automatisch als Spam markieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:202
msgid ""
"Automatically mark pingbacks and trackbacks as spam without OpenAI check"
msgstr ""
"Pingbacks und Trackbacks automatisch als Spam markieren, ohne OpenAI-Prüfung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:209
msgid "Mark Different Language as Spam"
msgstr "Andere Sprache als Spam markieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:215
msgid ""
"Automatically mark submissions as spam if they are in a different language "
"than your website (useful for single-language websites)"
msgstr ""
"Markieren Sie Beiträge automatisch als Spam, wenn sie in einer anderen "
"Sprache als Ihre Website verfasst sind (nützlich für einsprachige Websites)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:221
msgid "Language Mismatch Score Boost"
msgstr "Sprachinkongruenz-Score-Boost"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:230
msgid ""
"Amount to increase spam score when language doesn't match (0.1 - 1.0). "
"Default: 0.3"
msgstr ""
"Betrag zur Erhöhung der Spam-Bewertung, wenn die Sprache nicht übereinstimmt "
"(0,1 – 1,0). Standardwert: 0,3"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:236
msgid "Spam Blocked Message"
msgstr "Nachricht nach Übermittlung eines Spams"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:243
msgid ""
"Message displayed to users when spam is detected and submission is blocked. "
"Default: \"Thank you for your message.\""
msgstr ""
"Meldung, die Benutzern angezeigt wird, wenn Spam erkannt und die "
"Übermittlung blockiert wird. Standard: „Vielen Dank für Ihre Nachricht.“"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:250
msgid "OpenAI Integration"
msgstr "OpenAI-Integration"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:257
msgid "Enable OpenAI Detection"
msgstr "OpenAI-Erkennung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:263
msgid "Use OpenAI to detect spam"
msgstr "Verwenden Sie OpenAI, um Spam zu erkennen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:269
msgid "OpenAI API Key"
msgstr "OpenAI API-Schlüssel"

#. translators: %s: OpenAI API URL
#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:278
msgid ""
"Get your API key from <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">OpenAI Platform</a>"
msgstr ""
"API-Schlüssel von <a href=\"%s\" target=\"_blank\">der OpenAI-Plattform</a> "
"holen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:286
msgid "OpenAI Model"
msgstr "OpenAI-Modell"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:300
msgid "Which AI model to use for spam detection"
msgstr "Welches KI-Modell soll für die Spam-Erkennung verwendet werden?"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:306
msgid "AI Spam Threshold"
msgstr "KI-Spam-Schwellenwert"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:315
msgid ""
"Spam score threshold (0.0 - 1.0). Higher values mean fewer submissions are "
"flagged as spam (less strict). Lower values mean more submissions are "
"flagged as spam (more strict). Default: 0.7"
msgstr ""
"Spam-Score-Schwellenwert (0,0 – 1,0). Höhere Werte bedeuten, dass weniger "
"Beiträge als Spam markiert werden (weniger streng). Niedrigere Werte "
"bedeuten, dass mehr Beiträge als Spam markiert werden (strenger). "
"Standardwert: 0,7"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:322, includes/admin/class-settings.php:893
msgid "Heuristic Detection"
msgstr "Heuristische Erkennung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:329
msgid "Enable Heuristic Detection"
msgstr "Heuristische Erkennung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:335
msgid "Use local heuristics to detect spam patterns (works without OpenAI)"
msgstr ""
"Verwenden Sie lokale Heuristiken, um Spam-Muster zu erkennen (funktioniert "
"ohne OpenAI)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:341
msgid "Heuristic Spam Threshold"
msgstr "Heuristik-Spam-Schwellenwert"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:350
msgid "Spam score threshold for heuristic detection (0.0 - 1.0). Default: 0.6"
msgstr ""
"Spam-Score-Schwellenwert für heuristische Erkennung (0,0 – 1,0). Höher = "
"strenger. Standardwert: 0,7"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:356
msgid "Enable Link Check"
msgstr "Link-Prüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:362
msgid "Enable suspicious link detection"
msgstr "Erkennung verdächtiger Links aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:368
msgid "Enable Character Pattern Check"
msgstr "Zeichenmusterprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:374
msgid ""
"Enable suspicious character pattern detection (e.g., ALL CAPS, repeated "
"characters)"
msgstr ""
"Aktivieren Sie die Erkennung verdächtiger Zeichenmuster (z. B. alles in "
"GROSSBUCHSTABEN, wiederholte Zeichen)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:380
msgid "Enable Spam Phrase Check"
msgstr "Spam-Phrasenprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:386
msgid "Enable known spam phrase detection"
msgstr "Erkennung von Spam-Phrasen aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:392
msgid "Enable Email Pattern Check"
msgstr "E-Mail-Musterprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:398
msgid "Enable suspicious email pattern detection"
msgstr "Erkennung verdächtiger E-Mail-Muster aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:404
msgid "Enable Referrer Check"
msgstr "Referrer Prüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:410
msgid "Enable referrer analysis (missing or suspicious referrer detection)"
msgstr ""
"Referrer-Analyse aktivieren (Erkennung fehlender oder verdächtiger Referrer)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:416
msgid "Enable User Agent Check"
msgstr "User-Agent Prüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:422
msgid "Enable user agent analysis (bot and suspicious user agent detection)"
msgstr ""
"User Agent Analyse aktivieren (Bots und verdächtige User Agents erkennen)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:428
msgid "Enable Content Length Check"
msgstr "Inhaltslängenprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:434
msgid ""
"Enable content length analysis (very short or extremely long content "
"detection)"
msgstr ""
"Prüfung der Inhaltslänge aktivieren (sehr kurzer oder extrem langer Inhalt)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:440
msgid "Enable Mixed Script Check"
msgstr "Gemischte Zeichensatzprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:446
msgid ""
"Enable mixed script detection (different character sets like Cyrillic + "
"Latin)"
msgstr ""
"Aktivieren Sie die Erkennung gemischter Zeichensätze (unterschiedliche "
"Zeichensätze wie Kyrillisch + Lateinisch)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:452
msgid "Enable Unicode Anomalies Check"
msgstr "Zeichensatz-Anomalieprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:458
msgid ""
"Enable Unicode anomalies detection (zero-width characters, control "
"characters, homoglyphs)"
msgstr ""
"Unicode-Anomalienerkennung aktivieren (Zeichen ohne Breite, Steuerzeichen, "
"Homoglyphen)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:464
msgid "Enable Numbers/Letters Only Check"
msgstr "Nur Nummern-/Buchstabenprüfung aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:470
msgid "Enable detection of content containing only numbers or only letters"
msgstr ""
"Erkennung von Inhalten, die nur Zahlen oder nur Buchstaben enthalten, "
"aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:476
msgid "Enable IP Address in Content Check"
msgstr "Prüfung auf IP-Adressen im Inhalt aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:482
msgid "Enable detection of IP addresses in content (not in URLs)"
msgstr "Erkennung von IP-Adressen in Inhalten (nicht in URLs) aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:488
msgid "Enable Repeated Multilingual Content Check"
msgstr "Prüfung auf IP-Adressen im Inhalt aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:494
msgid ""
"Enable detection of repeated multilingual content (same message in multiple "
"languages separated by markers like ***)"
msgstr ""
"Erkennung von wiederholten mehrsprachigen Inhalten aktivieren (gleiche "
"Nachricht in mehreren Sprachen, getrennt durch Markierungen wie ***)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:501
msgid "Email Notifications"
msgstr "E-Mail Benachrichtigungen"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:508
msgid "Notification Email"
msgstr "Benachrichtigungsemail"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:515
msgid ""
"Email address to receive spam notifications. If empty, admin email will be "
"used."
msgstr ""
"E-Mail-Adresse für den Empfang von Spam-Benachrichtigungen. Wenn dieses Feld "
"leer ist, wird die E-Mail-Adresse des Administrators verwendet."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:521
msgid "Notification Type"
msgstr "Benachrichtigungsart"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:528
msgid "No notifications"
msgstr "Keine Benachrichtigungen"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:529
msgid "Immediate (on each spam detection)"
msgstr "Sofort (bei jeder Spam-Erkennung)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:530
msgid "Daily summary"
msgstr "Tägliche Zusammenfassung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:531
msgid "Weekly summary"
msgstr "Wöchentliche Zusammenfassung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:533
msgid "How often to receive spam notifications."
msgstr "Wie oft Spam-Benachrichtigungen empfangen werden sollen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:540, includes/admin/class-settings.php:905
msgid "Maintenance"
msgstr "Wartung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:547
msgid "Log Retention"
msgstr "Dauer der Protokollspeicherung"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:556
msgid "Days to keep logs (default: 30)"
msgstr "Tage, an denen Protokolle aufbewahrt werden (Standard: 30)"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:562
msgid "Keep Data on Uninstall"
msgstr "Daten bei Deinstallation behalten"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:568
msgid ""
"If enabled, all plugin data (options, submissions, statistics) will be kept "
"when the plugin is deleted. If disabled, all data will be permanently "
"deleted."
msgstr ""
"Wenn diese Option aktiviert ist, bleiben alle Plugin-Daten (Optionen, "
"Übermittlungen, Statistiken) beim Löschen des Plugins erhalten. Wenn diese "
"Option deaktiviert ist, werden alle Daten dauerhaft gelöscht."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:574
msgid "Enable GitHub Updates"
msgstr "Updates via Github aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:580
msgid ""
"Enable automatic updates from GitHub releases. <strong>Activate at your own "
"risk.</strong> Updates will be installed automatically without additional "
"confirmation."
msgstr ""
"Aktivieren Sie automatische Updates aus GitHub-Releases. <strong>Die "
"Aktivierung erfolgt auf eigene Gefahr.</strong> Updates werden automatisch "
"und ohne zusätzliche Bestätigung installiert."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:586
msgid "Enable Activity Log"
msgstr "Aktivitätsprotokoll aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:592
msgid ""
"Enable activity logging to track important plugin events (e.g., weekly "
"summaries sent, table maintenance)."
msgstr ""
"Aktivieren Sie die Aktivitätsprotokollierung, um wichtige Plugin-Ereignisse "
"zu verfolgen (z. B. versendete wöchentliche Zusammenfassungen, "
"Tabellenpflege)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:602
msgid "Configure general spam protection settings."
msgstr "Konfiguriere allgemeine Spam-Schutzeinstellungen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:610
msgid "Configure OpenAI integration for spam detection."
msgstr "OpenAI-Integration für die Spam-Erkennung."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:618
msgid "Configure local heuristic spam detection (works without OpenAI)."
msgstr ""
"Lokale heuristische Spam-Erkennung konfigurieren (funktioniert ohne OpenAI)."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:622
msgid "Enable All Checks"
msgstr "Alle Prüfungen aktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:625
msgid "Disable All Checks"
msgstr "Alle Prüfungen deaktivieren"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:664
msgid "Configure email notifications for spam detections."
msgstr "E-Mail-Benachrichtigungen für Spam-Erkennungen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:672
msgid "Configure maintenance and cleanup settings."
msgstr "Einstellungen für Wartung und Bereinigung."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:682
msgid "Email Notification Status:"
msgstr "E-Mail Benachrichtigungsstatus:"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:695
msgid "Daily summary: NOT SCHEDULED - Please save settings to schedule."
msgstr ""
"Tägliche Zusammenfassung: NICHT GEPLANT – Bitte speichern Sie die "
"Einstellungen, um einen Zeitplan zu erstellen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:691
msgid "Daily summary: Next scheduled for %s"
msgstr "Tägliche E-Mail-Zusammenfassung geplant für %s"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:710
msgid "Weekly summary: NOT SCHEDULED - Please save settings to schedule."
msgstr ""
"Wöchentliche Zusammenfassung: NICHT GEPLANT – Bitte Einstellungen speichern, "
"um zu planen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:706
msgid "Weekly summary: Next scheduled for %s"
msgstr "Wöchentliche E-Mail-Zusammenfassung: die nächste ist geplant für %s"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:718
msgid ""
"WARNING: WordPress cron is disabled. Email notifications will not work "
"unless you use a real cron job."
msgstr ""
"WARNUNG: WordPress Cron ist deaktiviert. E-Mail-Benachrichtigungen "
"funktionieren nur, wenn Sie einen echten Cron-Job verwenden."

#. translators: %s: Email address
#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:725
msgid "Notification email: %s"
msgstr "Benachrichtigungsemail: %s"

#. translators: %s: Link to Activity Log
#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:733
msgid "Check the %s for email delivery logs and debug information."
msgstr ""
"Überprüfen Sie die %s für E-Mail-Zustellungsprotokolle und Debug-"
"Informationen."

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:889
msgid "General"
msgstr "Allgemein"

#: includes/admin/class-settings.php:897
